TIME_BUCKET: Is the kickoff time early (noon or earlier), late (2 or later), or primetime (7pm or later)
HOME_GAME: Was the game a home game? 1= yes
REG_OR_POST: Regular season game? Or postseason game
YTG: Yards needed for a first down
COMPLETION: Was the pass caught, b1 rule?
RECEIVER_ID: What is the unique ID of the receiver?
YDS: Total yards for the completed pass, air + YAC
TD: Was the completed pass a touchdown? 1=1es
FIRST_DOWN: Did the completeion result in a first down? 1=1es
AIR_YDS: Yards the ball flew in the air to the receiver
YDS_AFTER_CATCH: Yards achieved by the receiver running with the ball
QB_POSITION: Where was the QB standing when the ball was snapped?
FIELD_TARGET: left sideline, left, middle, right, right sideline
